to compile, run the following commands:
$ mkdir -p cmake/build
$ cd cmake/build
$ cmake -DCMAKE_PREFIX_PATH=$MY_INSTALL_DIR ../..

All rubrics can be done using the same code and different command line arguments for the client.

./distsys_client takes 2 arguments:
1. Type of program one would like to run: (1) single request, single response. (2) single request, stream response, (3) stream request, single response, (4) stream request, stream response.
2. size of the string to pack in the message.


